#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Analyze return-addresses from dmalloc logfiles."
msgstr ""
"Analiza os enderezos de retorno a partir do ficheiros de rexistro de dmalloc."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extend_dmalloc</command> <group><option><replaceable>dmalloc-log</"
"replaceable> <command>binary</command></option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>extend_dmalloc</command> <group><option><replaceable>rexistro-de-"
"dmalloc</replaceable> <command>binario</command></option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descrición"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extend_dmalloc</command> will run <command>gdb</command>(1) to get "
"information on the return-addresses from a <command>dmalloc</command>(1) "
"logfile. Specifically it will examine any <literal>ra=</literal> lines and "
"try to get the corresponding line numbers"
msgstr ""
"<command>extend_dmalloc</command> executará <command>gdb</command>(1) para "
"extraer información sobre os enderezos de retorno non ficheiro de rexistro "
"de <command>dmalloc</command>(1). Examinará calquera liña <literal>ra=</"
"literal> e intentará obter os números de liña correspondentes"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The argument <option><command>binary</command></option> must be the binary "
"that generated the log <filename>dmalloc-log</filename>."
msgstr ""
"O argumento <option><command>binario</command></option> debe ser o binario "
"que xerase o <filename>rexistro-de-dmalloc-</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Esta utilidade forma parte do equipamento de desenvolvemento de programas de "
"&kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "Notas"

# skip-rule: proposta-contracción-de
#. Tag: para
#: man-extend_dmalloc.1.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may wish to direct the output from <command>extend_dmalloc</command> to "
"a file, since otherwise <command>gdb</command> seems to prompt for a return "
"as if you are at the end of a page."
msgstr ""
"Quizais queira dirixir a saída de <command>extend_dmalloc</command> a un "
"ficheiro, xa que doutro xeito <command>gdb</command> parece preguntar por un "
"retorno como se estivese no fin dunha páxina."

